{
  "stem": "58.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, you go in the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I raise the locomotive two, three inches, you pull the flatcar away, and I'm going to lower it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We pick up the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the locomotive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It hangs sideways.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't connect the-- the-- the chains right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we lower it again to the flatcar and we straighten it out a little bit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I told them how to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I pick this locomotive up, and the crane starts squeaking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I figure, any minute now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a wheel I turned slowly up to pick it up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I picked it up about two, three inches, and I say, you guys pull it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- this guy was sweating more than me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I let down the locomotive and I told him to push it in the right place to lower it on the-- on the rail.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We put it down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "From that day on, he brought me, every day, two slices of bread, about an inch thick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Two slices.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a couple cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we start bringing in-- the guys that worked in Skarzysko on this locomotive were there, and they right away went on this locomotive to start switching the cars.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Bringing in loaded cars to unload and the empties out to the station back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we worked there on this, but the-- I worked mostly on the outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we worked there for quite a while, until about 194-- end of 1944, beginning '45.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the same thing happened like in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How long does it take to go through Poland?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you go forward, just like the German went in-- the Germans went into Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you go in with power, it's moving ahead.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
